ndspore/blob/v2.8.0/mindspore/python/mindspore/ops/operations/debug_ops.py#L699\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#mindspore.ops.Print\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\"></a></dt>\n<dd><p>Print the inputs to stdout.</p>\n<p>Refer to <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"mindspore.ops.print_.html#mindspore.ops.print_\" title=\"mindspore.ops.print_\"><code class=\"xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">mindspore.ops.print_()</span></code></a> for more detail.</p>\n<dl class=\"simple\">\n<dt>Inputs:</dt><dd><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>input_x</strong> (Union[Tensor, bool, int, float, str]) - The graph node to attach to.\nSupports multiple inputs which are separated by ','.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n<dt>Outputs:</dt><dd><p>Tensor, has the same data type and shape as original <cite>input_x</cite>.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt>Supported Platforms:</dt><dd><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">Ascend</span></code> <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">GPU</span></code> <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">CPU</span></code></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"doctest highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">numpy</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">np</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">mindspore</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">nn</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ops</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"k\">class</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">PrintDemo</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">nn</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Cell</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>    <span class=\"k\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"fm\">__init__</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>        <span class=\"nb\">super</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">PrintDemo</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"fm\">__init__</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>        <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">print</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">ops</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Print</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">...</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>    <span class=\"k\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">construct</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>        <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'Print Tensor x and Tensor y:'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>        <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">...</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ones</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">])</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">astype</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">int32</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ones</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">])</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">astype</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">int32</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">net</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">PrintDemo</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">result</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">net</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">Print Tensor x and Tensor y:</span>\n<span class=\"go\">Tensor(shape=[2, 1], dtype=Int32, value=</span>\n<span class=\"go\">[[1],</span>\n<span class=\"go\"> [1]])</span>\n<span class=\"go\">Tensor(shape=[2, 2], dtype=Int32, value=</span>\n<span class=\"go\">[[1, 1],</span>\n<span class=\"go\"> [1, 1]])</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</dd></dl>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<footer><div aria-label=\"Footer\" class=\"rst-footer-buttons\" role=\"navigation\">\n<a accesskey=\"p\" class=\"btn btn-neutral float-left\" href=\"mindspore.ops.TensorDump.html\" rel=\"prev\" title=\"mindspore.ops.TensorDump\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-a